, then step back and canni while my DPS continues ... hehe<br><br>2hb (retired - perhaps my best straight up weapon though) : <a href=HTTP://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=9012 target=_new>Rod of Virtue</a><br>Dmg 30, Dly 35. +10 Str +10 Sta +15 Wis +15 vsMg +15 vsFire +15 vsCold +15 vsPos +15 vsDis +50 HP +100 Mana +8.20 Wt  <br><br>Edit: added sig and stars(whoops)<br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Apr 11 12:38:50 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=120263 target=_new>- Paghk Heyokah'Zek, Morell-Thule</a></td></td></tr>
